{
  "stem": "22972.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And somehow or other, my mother talked them out of arresting my dad, and-- and they came back out and we drove away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah, there were many times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was a night when my father was late, and my father-- you know, it got later and later and later and my mother stood-- and I stood on our balcony, quietly, not talking.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and I was scared to death.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I finally-- I apparently said to my mother-- I must have been 12, 13.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I finally said to my mother, I said, when they arrest a man, do they call you and tell you?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was all I had to say to my mother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, she-- you know-- became ballistic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And half an hour later, my father came waltzing in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we saw his car driving up and my mother pulled me away so that he wouldn't see that we'd been standing on the balcony like Madama Butterfly and Suzuki, waiting for him.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had gone to his stamp dealer who had found a very, very rare stamp and he forgot about the time, and-- and he was late.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, we were always worried.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If somebody was 10 minutes late, when there was a-- a knock on the door, when there was-- of course, we lived with Damocles's sword hanging over us.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We never knew what the next day would bring.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I-- I-- I started-- it-- it brought to mind something else and that was two other things.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In 1936, we went to Berlin and-- we went to London, to England for the summer, and we had a sewing room in-- in our apartment.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You didn't go to a store to buy clothes.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
